**@xgopilot** (Oct 27, 07:45)
### Task Completed ✅

Successfully implemented the missing NULL cipher packet handling changes from the reference commit.

### Changes Made

**1. srtcp.go** ([srtcp.go:23-67](https://github.com/kingqn0321/srtp/blob/927caa9/srtcp.go#L23-L67))
- Moved `srtcpHeaderSize` constant to separate line for better code organization
- Added `allocateIfMismatch(dst, encrypted)` call before `cipher.decryptRTCP`
- This critical change ensures SRTCP packets with encryption bit cleared (E=0) are properly processed with authentication tag validation and protocol field removal

**2. util.go** ([util.go:42-61](https://github.com/kingqn0321/srtp/blob/927caa9/util.go#L42-L61))
- Implemented `allocateIfMismatch` function for smart buffer allocation
- Uses `isSameBuffer` check to detect shared buffers and avoid unnecessary copying
- Handles same-buffer optimization correctly for performance

